{
  "stem": "19231.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I told them I lost my parents, and I'm all alone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were very, you know, they gave me some money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They left before me to Poland or to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They left, because they were all the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He probably had money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because some people, you know, had-- made money on the black market.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the people handled things different than I did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when they left, they met-- they left to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they met my brother there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said to them, you know, I know where your sister is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She is in Tashkent and so and so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, they called me to the office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told me that I have a telegram-- that was already after the war-- that I have a telegram.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was my two brothers' name that they are alive and they wish I can come there so and so, you know, the address, if I can come real soon.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I know I have two brothers still alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I still couldn't go till the government will send me out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have no connection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did you feel inside when you--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was jumping on the-- I went on my bed, and I was jumping and dancing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a big holiday, you know, that I have two brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at least I know I have somebody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they send me-- when they start sending out the people from Russia, I went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent us to a-- to a town in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole [NON-ENGLISH], they call-- the whole train went to one place, you know, they sent us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
